{"tid":582130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行山夫婦馬鞍山吊手岩 報稱遇上老虎","createTime":"2018-03-06T02:06:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T03:21:40.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fa8b1b12c6af573071f7c97022b51ed4b06bc36e","tid":582130,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T02:06:22.000Z","msg":"一對夫婦早上近9時在馬鞍山吊手岩郊遊徑行山時，報稱發現疑似老虎，大驚下報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n夫婦稱行山期間，發現一頭懷疑老虎的貓科類動物在樹叢出沒。警方及消防員登山救援，並搜捕虎蹤。<br />\n<br />\n吊手岩高588米，屬牛押山西脊，爲香港著名險峰之一，現被劃入馬鞍山郊野公園。"},{"pid":"053be53a81359cd4da5c30513543c9fab366e987","tid":582130,"uid":53790,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T02:06:59.000Z","msg":"老虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9f846b050284cda975df989dca6cc5fb104455","tid":582130,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T02:07:05.000Z","msg":"鳩up無極限<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d88746cd5c95ea55f3cc641ae20a7706ae0e17d","tid":582130,"uid":153400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T02:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198877fcbd92fd910b88ab5d3b9d61bf7ab21b5f","tid":582130,"uid":6604,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T02:07:52.000Z","msg":"佢老婆咪係老虎囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2141b5d0417f4a8626719384b34044a57e179937","tid":582130,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T02:09:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6bd6ec8f3bf789ad39da9f5e746cac675f58ff1","tid":582130,"uid":63845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci